title: ParTrend Me Boy, Is That The Zeitanooga Cheug Cheug 6/7: Matthew McConaughey, Bechdel Test, Orangutan, Day N Vegas, Great Salt Lake, Rolling Stone
itunes:title: ParTrend Me Boy, Is That The Zeitanooga Cheug Cheug 6/7: Matthew McConaughey, Bechdel Test, Orangutan, Day N Vegas, Great Salt Lake, Rolling Stone
description:
In this edition of ParTrend Me Boy, Is That The Zeitanooga Cheug Cheug, Jack and Miles discuss Matthew McConaughey advocating for gun control, 'Fire Island' not passing the Bechdel Test?, an orangutan attack at a zoo, the Day N Vegas lineup, the Great Salt Lake drying up, and Rolling Stone's top 200 Hip-Hop albums of all-time!
